{"tid":2190063,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"創新及科技局：港康碼將載有市民個人資料轉移至內地","createTime":"2020-09-05T10:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T17:34:45.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":148,"uniUserReply":59,"replies":[{"pid":"02a17de1eec7338c5e5213b3f76f1a1d51ba1ea2","tid":2190063,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:31:40.000Z","msg":"被斥拒封關而導致疫情爆發的港府，原來早在第三波疫情爆發前已為香港健康碼鋪路。創新及科技局局長薛永恒指，政府早在5、6月已準備好通關用的港康碼，惟出現第三波疫情，才未有如期推展。港康碼將載有市民個人資料，亦會將資料轉移至內地。當疫情一穩定，港康碼就會進行。另外，當局正研發「感染風險通知」手機應用程式，透過掃瞄「二維碼」記錄行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/27ITYCW5D5ECVMBWSPAIB3KO6Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2F27ITYCW5D5ECVMBWSPAIB3KO6Y%2F&d=bvaV6%2BUCrkGuzNdoarVmR8orGdVmFuHsJRpnpeioS7U%3D&h=24dc62da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2F27ITYCW5D5ECVMBWSPAIB3KO6Y%2F&h=13c097df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/27ITYCW5D5ECVMBWSPAIB3KO6Y/</a>"},{"pid":"b133b440fd66dcc856eb89086da2b014b9769289","tid":2190063,"uid":11454,"like":90,"dislike":2,"score":88,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"樓本愈政府否認， 就愈代表係真<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n信政府真係蠢過豬"},{"pid":"ce93b52cd32db1b985511bea7a84e93fd81d37df","tid":2190063,"uid":122275,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:34:27.000Z","msg":"好撚高科技啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e19847abf9666630b2cc976235cff62c961f8802","tid":2190063,"uid":21545,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:35:15.000Z","msg":"一早估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0d33e65bf2c67b378abffd7657c6f62696b7995","tid":2190063,"uid":21545,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T10:35:50.000Z","msg":"祝班做檢測嘅on9好運<img src=\"/